Type: Package
Package: mut2
Title: Reversible mutation matrices and pairwise likelihood ratios
Version: 1.1
Date: 2023-04-16
Authors@R: c(
    person("Thore", "Egeland", , "thore.egeland@nmbu.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3465-8885"))
  )
Description: The mutation matrix is made reversible using three versions of 
    the Metropolis - Hastings algorithm. The Thompson pairwise likelihood
    is extended to include mutations.
Maintainer: Thore Egeland <Thore.Egeland@nmbu.no>
